## Tech Stack Decision
- **Frontend**: app.waickoff.com (Vite + React + Mantine)
- **API**: api.waickoff.com (FastAPI + Claude integration)
- **Database**: MongoDB + Redis
- **AI**: Claude Sonnet 4 API (dentro de la API)

## Quick Commands
```bash
# Docker Development 🐳
scripts\wadm-dev.bat start              # Start complete stack
scripts\wadm-dev.bat status             # Check all services
scripts\wadm-dev.bat logs               # View API logs

# API Testing
curl -H "X-API-Key: wadm-master-key-2024" \
  "http://localhost:8000/api/v1/indicators/volume-profile/BTCUSDT"

# Create API Key
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/keys \
  -H "X-API-Key: wadm-master-key-2024" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name": "Test Key", "permissions": ["read"]}'

# URLs
http://localhost:8000                   # API Base
http://localhost:8000/api/docs          # Swagger UI
http://localhost:3000                   # Frontend (próximamente)
```

## Business Model Summary
- **Pricing**: $1 per session (24h or 100k tokens)
- **Packages**: $5-$80 (mejor valor en bulk)
- **Margin**: 55% en precio base
- **Target**: $15k MRR en mes 1
- **Payment**: Deferred - Focus on MVP features

